  # Zenodo, so this is the right DOI for "cite this software" references
  # that should track future releases.
  - type: doi
    value: 10.5281/zenodo.20259146
    description: "Concept DOI (all versions) — Zenodo archive of the QMaxent source code."
  # Version-specific DOI for v0.1.7. Use this for citations that must
